    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "A similar error occurs if you put a raw hyperlink as the value for the <code>@see</code> tag in your javadoc.  To fix it in this case wrap the hyperlink in an html anchor element: <code>&#47;** @see &lt;a href=&quot;http:&#47;&#47;example.com&quot;&gt;Example&lt;&#47;a&gt; *&#47;</code>"
  } ],
